query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `bulk_update_affected_items` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	`bulkUpdateId` int NOT NULL,
	`assessmentId` int NOT NULL,
	`projectId` int NOT NULL,
	`componentCode` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
	`previousServiceLife` int,
	`newServiceLife` int NOT NULL,
	`createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	INDEX `idx_affected_bulk_update` (`bulkUpdateId`),
	INDEX `idx_affected_assessment` (`assessmentId`),
	INDEX `idx_affected_project` (`projectId`)
);
